.TH term-profile "1" "October 2025" "SMI Toolset 0.100.0" "SMI Terminal Command"
.SH NAME
term-profile \- Create or edit an SMI terminal profile
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B term-profile
.I PROFILE_NAME
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
.B term-profile
allows creating and editing SMI terminal profiles.
If the specified \fIPROFILE_NAME\fR does not exist in \fB~/.term/\fR, it tries to copy a base template from the system profiles directory.
The script then opens the profile file using the \fBnano\fR editor for customization.
.SH AUTHOR
.PP
Command written by Imre Tabur.
Documentation written by Imre Tabur.
